title: RPLA - RPLA (1994)
description:
RPLA: Very controversial band that graced the Kerrang! cover in '93
when their album came out on EMI records! 
This album is really good in my opinion. It reminds me of the Cult,
especially in the vocal department.
It's a shame they didn't have more opportunities to make more records.

01. Metal Queen Hijack
02. The Absolute Queen Of Pop 
03. City Of Angels
04. Loving You Is A Dirty Job (But Somebody's Gotta Do It)
05. Unnatural Woman 
06. The Bomb And The Gun
07. Last Night A Drag Queen Saved Your Life
08. U.K. Rock City
09. Something To Live And Breathe By 
10. Vagabond Sister
11. Hair Of The Dog (That Bit Me) 
12. Hold Back The Storm 

Enjoy!!
